COMMENT: smooth movement script by itdeer, feel free to use with credit

*5Aa4(9oAc}Hj7hP5gjI: She will head to the left or right hall. Close the door on her until she leaves
She will enter your office ignoring your doors. Shock her to get rid of her
Take a picture of her when she's in a camera. The camera she's on will be marked
She will randomly appear in the left or right hall. Click the tophat button and select which hall she's in
Her temper will slowly tick down. Make sure to regurally use the refill button on the camera she's on to reset it
She will appear in your office while your camera is up. Click on her before she kill you
Turtlebot likes to follow Bowt around. Make sure to move Bowt out of the room it's in when Turtlebot moves
When she's in your office, shock her. She is slower than Shock, but will move around in the office
Close the door on her when she gets to a hall. She is slower than Swing but makes no sound cue
If the doors ever break, they will stay permanantly broken
Swing has a high chance of staying at the same door instead of moving. This still resets her kill timer
Swave only shows the order numbers on her screen and flashing the wrong camera kills you
Only some infected cameras get reset when all of them are infected
Znyufm8$En{N3i}E,`4o: Instead of heading back when you use the door on her, she will just immediately go to the other one
If you spend too much time in the cameras while she's waiting to enter the office, she'll just kill you
Swave will be in 3 cameras at once. Flash her in the right order indicated by the numbers on the cameras
Pam makes no cue when attacking
The refill button only refills a third of her temper
She takes longer to kill you, but clicking her only partially resets her kill timer
Cameras Turtlebot visits become infected. If it ever revisit an infected camera then it'll kill you
She moves around much more erratically in the room
When you close the door on her, she will enter your office and move around erratically. Click on her
If the doors ever break, they will stay permanantly broken
Swing has a high chance of staying at the same door instead of moving. This still resets her kill timer
Swave only shows the order numbers on her screen and flashing the wrong camera kills you
Only some infected cameras get reset when all of them are infected
